The paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques to improve the spatial resolution of multispectral images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves wavelet-based methods, which are commonly used in graphics and image processing, suggesting cs.GR (Graphics) as the second likely category. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Machine Learning). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves statistical methods, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
